pageContext.claim: “New polling shows that the totally partisan Impeachment Hoax is going nowhere. A vast majority want the Do Nothing Democrats to move on to other things now!”
pageContext.analysis: Polls show support for Trump's impeachment is higher than opposition to impeachment, according to 538. In fact, it wasn't until September, when the House announced an impeachment inquiry, that support for impeachment surpassed opposition in public polling.
